{"tid":1627214,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請暫停升級暴力","createTime":"2019-10-05T15:00:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T16:08:09.000Z","uid":185762,"like":7,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"61d68b4bca8f3fcc28387c79e10f79712da25261","tid":1627214,"uid":185762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T15:00:04.000Z","msg":"唔係叫你地唔好裝修 唔好出神獸<br />\n而事實上文宣上已經追唔上我地嘅升級<br />\n<br />\n由爆黨鐵開始已經有啲師奶開始問我點解要破壞 有好多人仲未習慣到 亦未明白 我住果到仍然有好多街坊有好多野係完全唔清楚 甚至本來黃嘅人都追唔上<br />\n<br />\n本來解釋比一啲立場唔同嘅人知<br />\n係一樣好需要耐性同時間嘅野<br />\n<br />\n所以<br />\n裝修可以繼續 神獸可以照出<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但請只繼續對準美心 黨鐵同福建幫</span></span></strong><br />\n升級去中資企業希望可以暫一暫停<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">文宣上集中幫忙仍然較藍嘅區域</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">connect番我地自己嘅手足！</span></span></strong><br />\n其有好多人已經放棄咗連登 <br />\n平時對自己人都下下屌人老母<br />\n想升級嘅人可以問下大家意見先討論下<br />\n唔認同嘅都可以客氣少少嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n呢場係一場香港人嘅時代革命<br />\n我地要嘅唔單止勇氣同智慧<br />\n更需要每個人嘅支持 <br />\n要繼續行落去就更需要更多嘅香港人支持<br />\n<br />\n單憑熱血同公義係唔足以撼動呢個政權<br />\n背後嘅人民卻可以俾到我哋力量同勇氣 <br />\n去繼續同霸權對抗<br />\n<br />\n我哋要改變更多嘅人企喺我地同一陣線<br />\n而唔係創造更多嘅敵人"},{"pid":"e36e6b0ff98208bc478ac2e1eeecb311801ef971","tid":1627214,"uid":185762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T15:01:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"72e02973cc3e749d6af92a537dc2f31fac71ceff","tid":1627214,"uid":185762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T15:01:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e0c4d83faa4488f614692e939397c17c62940881","tid":1627214,"uid":185762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T15:01:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"35d3c7dcd25d4b0aad37ac02211a6ed61f9f4c43","tid":1627214,"uid":185762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T15:01:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"42b8e8dd409c918ddae4823cb311d755509081e9","tid":1627214,"uid":185762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T15:02:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b2e204a31b71aaa77c2fb355dc9a522ba6c9b6c7","tid":1627214,"uid":312672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61d68b4bca8f3fcc28387c79e10f79712da25261","tid":1627214,"uid":185762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T15:00:04.000Z","msg":"唔係叫你地唔好裝修 唔好出神獸<br />\n而事實上文宣上已經追唔上我地嘅升級<br />\n<br />\n由爆黨鐵開始已經有啲師奶開始問我點解要破壞 有好多人仲未習慣到 亦未明白 我住果到仍然有好多街坊有好多野係完全唔清楚 甚至本來黃嘅人都追唔上<br />\n<br />\n本來解釋比一啲立場唔同嘅人知<br />\n係一樣好需要耐性同時間嘅野<br />\n<br />\n所以<br />\n裝修可以繼續 神獸可以照出<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但請只繼續對準美心 黨鐵同福建幫</span></span></strong><br />\n升級去中資企業希望可以暫一暫停<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">文宣上集中幫忙仍然較藍嘅區域</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">connect番我地自己嘅手足！</span></span></strong><br />\n其有好多人已經放棄咗連登 <br />\n平時對自己人都下下屌人老母<br />\n想升級嘅人可以問下大家意見先討論下<br />\n唔認同嘅都可以客氣少少嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n呢場係一場香港人嘅時代革命<br />\n我地要嘅唔單止勇氣同智慧<br />\n更需要每個人嘅支持 <br />\n要繼續行落去就更需要更多嘅香港人支持<br />\n<br />\n單憑熱血同公義係唔足以撼動呢個政權<br />\n背後嘅人民卻可以俾到我哋力量同勇氣 <br />\n去繼續同霸權對抗<br />\n<br />\n我哋要改變更多嘅人企喺我地同一陣線<br />\n而唔係創造更多嘅敵人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T15:02:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>用聰明方法, 長期抗爭, 保護自己人身安全</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/u-Bucmv0Jhg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fu-Bucmv0Jhg&d=AECyLZWdcqpY%2FGgvZN2GpHGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=ae595c02\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/u-Bucmv0Jhg</a>"},{"pid":"630c190c2732c3112e8fc9fe04f36f7b5c92f632","tid":1627214,"uid":73915,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T15:02:13.000Z","msg":"你係咪唔知咩叫國企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a14384621f94ebdebff432c29703983046825e81","tid":1627214,"uid":185762,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"630c190c2732c3112e8fc9fe04f36f7b5c92f632","tid":1627214,"uid":73915,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T15:02:13.000Z","msg":"你係咪唔知咩叫國企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T15:05:03.000Z","msg":"你知 我知 單眼佬都知 但係唔係個個師奶都知<br />\n之前用左咁多時間先令佢哋知警暴<br />\n唔想短時間嘅升級 失去佢哋嘅支持"},{"pid":"bd9f4caf75070944a48f8a9f29c2170980adfc4e","tid":1627214,"uid":195998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T15:05:44.000Z","msg":"lmao"},{"pid":"7a89a6d3740d7d9d1720597f316e96054a6a14ee","tid":1627214,"uid":55956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T15:07:17.000Z","msg":"武力*"},{"pid":"a4f295f0fdbeda7b944ca22376ef7567092dbb5c","tid":1627214,"uid":185762,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T15:08:35.000Z","msg":"我哋要嘅唔係武力嘅升級 而係文宣上嘅升級<br />\n唔好再ff連儂牆之前嘅成功<br />\n政府嘅文宣又已經再升級 <br />\n我哋唔可以滿足而家嘅階段"},{"pid":"66b4aa63b99e651aa4c7c6de81cdafab85224438","tid":1627214,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T15:08:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />福建幫係中聯辦嘅組織嚟 佢都係中資其中一員 係咪唔好搞住"},{"pid":"cf2cc0ff4acde6a9555402174dd23c12f6da5696","tid":1627214,"uid":9542,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T15:09:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1mexyDa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1mexyDa.png&h=365657f6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ee0f41cb713b6a2de0e9bd21ccffbe7be146afc9","tid":1627214,"uid":185762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66b4aa63b99e651aa4c7c6de81cdafab85224438","tid":1627214,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T15:08:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />福建幫係中聯辦嘅組織嚟 佢都係中資其中一員 係咪唔好搞住"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T15:11:13.000Z","msg":"我指本來打緊果啲<br />\n再者唔好再升級去其他住<br />\n例如m記 Pacific cafe果啲"},{"pid":"ac84def84c69664b2782a798423c1a7ae054001e","tid":1627214,"uid":263667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T15:12:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n學界外國戰線一路努力緊同外國政府進行遊說工作，包括去美國國會支持《人權法》等等<br />\n而佢地而家需要繼續籌備其他國家既策略，需要人手做research，writing等等<br />\n希望大家能夠支持佢地既工作，眾籌目標只係300萬！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一人10蚊都捐爆啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">一齊click入去,多多益善少少無拘！</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fhkiad-crowdfunding%2F&d=AECyLZWdcqpY%2FGgvZN2GpHGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=66328136\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/</a><br />\n<br />\n呢個係香港大專學界國際事務代表團發表既眾籌official Facebook post，以正真身！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/107625880571519/posts/131825941484846?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F107625880571519%2Fposts%2F131825941484846%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=AECyLZWdcqpY%2FGgvZN2GpHGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=595ab5c1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/107625880571519/posts/131825941484846?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n願榮光歸香港！"},{"pid":"b2323e91c3b06336300614af2aa5323c8132d5e7","tid":1627214,"uid":330823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T15:18:32.000Z","msg":"我深藍的.<br />\n紅色資産本身就是黄屍主要敵人,所以我地連登藍絲一定要團結帶風向叫班黄屍唔好去攪.連登藍絲加油"},{"pid":"00744a268c1b92450f74757034b3215549e6cb81","tid":1627214,"uid":105976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T15:26:51.000Z","msg":"其實係要俾多少少時間街坊消化資訊"},{"pid":"9641a753f365b368fc7840ef4f6b56ea65dcae5a","tid":1627214,"uid":263577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T15:29:26.000Z","msg":"請大家訂立軍規<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1625399\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1625399</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d4024793d24ee682fb70b2243e8698ced1c69f4c","tid":1627214,"uid":185762,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"00744a268c1b92450f74757034b3215549e6cb81","tid":1627214,"uid":105976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T15:26:51.000Z","msg":"其實係要俾多少少時間街坊消化資訊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T15:38:36.000Z","msg":"之前啲人講咗好多次都冇人信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b05ee5555787bebd3bfedf828025be84efdf85b","tid":1627214,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T15:40:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"99cfb113700d9059229d2dffe2815b18c43053ec","tid":1627214,"uid":58041,"li